'''Mbhazima Samuel (Sam) Shilowa''' (b [[April 30|30 April]] [[1958|1958]]) ke tonakgolo ya [[Gauteng|Gauteng]], [[Afrika Borwa|Afrika Borwa]].

Shilowa o belegwe Olifantshoek yeo lehono e elego [[Limpopo|Limpopo]]. O phetile dithuto tša gage Akani High School ka [[1978|1978]]. Ngwageng o latelago  aya [[Johannesburg|Johannesburg]] go nyaka mošomo. O thomile go šoma John Weinberg Hardware [[Germiston|Germiston]]. Go tloga mowe aya [[Anglo Alpha Cement|Anglo Alpha Cement]]  [[Roodepoort|Rooderpoort]], morago  aya PSG Services - Johannesburg. ka  1981, Shilowa e bile leloko la mokgatlo wa babereki. O kgethilwe goba motlatša moperesidente morago yaba moperesidente wa [[SATAWU|South African Transport and Allied Workers Union]].

Ka 1999 o kgethilwe goba tonakgolo ya [[Gauteng|Gauteng]].

